<h1>Amazon - Price</h1>

<p>2014-02-25 00:16 Tuesday</p>

<p><a href="http://aws.amazon.com/cn/" target="_blank">http://aws.amazon.com/cn/</a></p>

<p>今日查到之前每月 $3.5 的扣费原因：</p>

<table border="1" cellpadding="3" cellspacing="1">
	<tbody>
		<tr>
			<td>$0.10 per GB-month of provisioned storage</td>
			<td>35.000 GB-Mo</td>
			<td>3.50</td>
		</tr>
	</tbody>
</table>

<p>然后把所有的 EC2 清理后终止掉了。</p>

