	<li>右上角&ldquo;我的帐户&rdquo;-&gt;&nbsp;<a href="https://portal.aws.amazon.com/gp/aws/manageYourAccount" target="_blank">https://portal.aws.amazon.com/gp/aws/manageYourAccount</a></li>
	<li>Account Activity&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;<a href="https://portal.aws.amazon.com/gp/aws/developer/account" target="_blank">https://portal.aws.amazon.com/gp/aws/developer/account</a></li>
	<li>或者使用新的&ldquo;帐单控制台&rdquo; -&gt;&nbsp;<a href="https://console.aws.amazon.com/billing/home" target="_blank">https://console.aws.amazon.com/billing/home</a></li>
</ol>

<h3>New Billing Console</h3>

